comments: Garland (CLE) establishes himself in Caruso's (CHI) path and his left leg remains within the frame of his body as contact occurs, which he does not deliver.
Mitchell (CLE) jumps toward Caruso's (CHI) back during the rebound and dislodges him from his position as he pursues the loose ball.
Vucevic (CHI) and Allen (CLE) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs as Allen moves off ball.
Drummond (CHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard Allen (CLE). He then moves to imminently guard Mobley (CLE).
Caruso (CHI) and Mitchell (CLE) briefly engage and disengage during the throw-in and the contact between the two players is marginal.
Garland (CLE) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs with White's (CHI) left arm prior to the release of his pass.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Vucevic (CHI) touches the ball last before it goes OOB.
DeRozan (CHI) commits a take foul on Garland (CLE).
Strus (CLE) delivers body contact to White (CLE) that re-routes him as he moves off ball.
Dosunmu (CHI) commits a take foul on Mitchell (CLE).
Mobley (CLE) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with White's (CHI) right arm prior to release.
